      <c01 level="series">
        <did>
          <unittitle>Administrative files</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Administrative files consist primarily of the files of Stated Clerk Robert Moreland who oversaw the administration of the presbytery in the period up to the time of its dissolution. The dates of most of these files are roughly from 1958 to 1961. Though the record group is devoid of such administrative information for previous decades, these files do provide a glimpse of the activities of the presbytery during the 1950s, especially the workings of the individual departments within the presbytery. Departments especially well documented in this series include Christian Education, Ministerial Relations, and Stewardship and Promotion.</p>
        </scopecontent>
